Then I should see the page in web editor with name "duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" & slug "/duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" display in list "Pages"
When I rename page in web editor name from "JIT001bWebPage" to "invalid<>?@#$updateJIT001bWebPage" & slug "empty"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Special characters are not allowed"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename page in web editor name from "JIT001bWebPage" to "empty" & slug "empty"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name is required"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename page in web editor name from "JIT001bWebPage" to "duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" & slug "empty"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "The Name has been taken, please use a different one"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename page in web editor name from "JIT001bWebPage" to "updateJIT001bWebPage" & slug "/updateJIT001bWebPage"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "updateJIT001bWebPage" & slug "/updateJIT001bWebPage" display in list "Pages"
